    "prompt": "Construct a program which calculates the base raised to the power of the non-negative exponent.",
    "source_code": "base = 2\nexp = 5\nif exp == 0 and base == 0 or exp < 0:\n    print(\"Error!\")\nelse:\n    result = 1\n    i = 1\n    while i <= exp:\n        result = result * base\n        i += 1\n    print(result)\n"
